    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Check out this dependable ride! It\u2019s a solid, honest car that\u2019s ready to get you where you need to go. While it shows some character from its time on the road and could use a little bit of extra love to shine, it remains a practical and reliable choice for anyone seeking great value. It's a perfect opportunity to own a well-used vehicle that still has plenty of life left in it!",
      "price": 19500.0,
